title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show FEB-07-2014 FRI
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show FEB-07-2014 FRI...PODCAST




The Glenn Beck Program



The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET



        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 2/7/14Friday, February 07, 2014


Glenn is sad to see Jay Leno leave the Tonight Show 
  and he remembers his personal experience with Jay 
    with a tribute to his time on the air. 

 Also, KY Senator Rand Paul joins the program to discuss his thoughts 
    on the state of America as well as the 2016 election.


  Plus, audio from yesterdays IRS hearing in D.C. that you must hear.
